      <title>亚德尼称，到 2025 年，中国仍“不具备投资潜力”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/china-is-still-uninvestable-in-2025-yardeni-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yardeni Research 总裁 Ed Yardeni 表示，尽管政府采取措施提振经济，但中国仍然“不值得投资”。Yardeni 还告诉彭博社的“与哈斯琳达·阿明的洞察”节目，一些美国企业不再将中国视为机遇之地。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/china-is-still-uninvestable-in-2025-yardeni-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币兑其他货币上涨表明中国的防御措施可能适得其反</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/yuan-s-rally-versus-peers-suggests-china-s-defense-can-backfire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对在岸人民币的严格控制正在产生意想不到的副作用，阻碍其重振经济的努力——出口商的竞争力减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/yuan-s-rally-versus-peers-suggests-china-s-defense-can-backfire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 05:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银财富敦促中国股票投资者保持“防御性”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/ubs-wealth-urges-chinese-stock-investors-to-stay-defensive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银全球财富管理表示，中国股市投资者应“保持防御态势”，因为消费依然疲软，而且随着唐纳德·特朗普即将提高关税，波动性预计会上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/ubs-wealth-urges-chinese-stock-investors-to-stay-defensive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 05:52:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
